                  <h2 >What's this Website about and how to use it?</h2>
                  <br>
                  <div class="lead ">
                     Have you ever been in a situation where you had to ask your friend or family member or even your neighbour for a favour as to buy you some items from the grocery store or supermarket, since they were already going there and it would save you both time and fuel to not go there or maybe just because you're too lazy. Or maybe you could have been in the other person's shoes, with an intent of helping them out and thinking that it would be really nice if you could buy some items for them as well.<br>
                     &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Well, it doesn't matter if you're doing it for saving fuel and/or the environment, or you're too lazy to buy items yourself, or you just wish to help out your mom or dad sometimes. We’ve all faced this problem in our daily lives one way or another, and it would be really nice to just tell someone or ask them without the need of calling or messaging them everytime.
                     <br>
                     &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
                     Thus, we present to you ‘SharePod’, a web app designed to help you out with the daily need of pooling and sharing list of items that are to be bought among your friends, family or colleagues.  
                  </div>
